Text:
Hej! cdomeij tack än än gång!
Har du nån aning om Centennial eller Coloradosagan som den hette finns på DVD?
Har bara en dassig divx version.
Tackar så mycket.. Dessa är gamla godingar. Har läst böckerna flera ggr.

All the parts of "War and Remembrance" show quite good "health," but parts 8, 9, and 11 have "0" health. Could some kind soul - or souls - out there pleeeeeeeease seed these parts? A LOT of people would be VERY grateful to you.

I'll be seeding this to 1:1, then hope someone else can take over as I need to make room. I think even though people sometimes tend to seed just a proportion of what they leech, these torrents need as much help as they can get!
So please everyone, seed as much as you take.
